// Milestone 3: Basic expressions and operators
// Test arithmetic, logical, and comparison operations

// Arithmetic expressions
1 + 2
5 - 3
4 * 6
10 / 2
7 % 3
2 ** 3

// Comparison expressions
5 > 3
10 < 20
x == y
a != b
count >= 0
value <= 100

// Logical expressions
true && false
x || y
!flag

// Parentheses and precedence
(1 + 2) * 3
2 + 3 * 4
a && (b || c)

// Variable expressions
x + y
name + " Smith"
count * 2